{
  "stem": "18294.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The theater that I used to go is there, it's still there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A lot of places what you still can recognize.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But these were built-- out of Vilna is all high-rising flats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It used to be all the little houses, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's what the character with Vilna was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now it's-- it's completely changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The old city, the old city is still there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So when you're going by car, you have to pay 50 [NON-ENGLISH] there for-- for Russian money, for to go into-- to the old city, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because most of them is in new city, everything built up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And did you see any people that you knew from before?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went-- no, I didn't see the people from before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was still one synagogue left in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went in, and we find there the shamus, was provided with-- and the synagogue was rebuilt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he told us, there is-- 8,000 or 8,000 Jews still in Vilna, not Vilna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But from around Vilna, from Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a lot of them, they was-- immigrate to-- to Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we wanted to go-- to go in another place, where there was a-- there was only back yard from the shul.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The shul was closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a goya there, a Polish woman there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she said, look, you can't go in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because it's closed, the shul.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So then we had a-- with a car, we went, and it was on the Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was-- have them prayer there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we go in there, and then we find some people what we know, not much.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
